results.description: This beautifull small animal( half an inch) lives in Azia, I did several attempts to get a nice picture of this animal but it is so hard to find one and to make a nice picture it,s even harder. But this time my diveguide found one at 25 meters dept while diving in the Philipinnes. Our divecomputer told us that we had 9 minutes to take the picture. The first minutes this seahorse was moving all the times and could not focus on him. Then he curled his tiny tail around the coral and i made some shots. With 1 minute to go we went up and finally i had my picture.
